So it proves that Shri Ganesha incarnated as Christ

27:01.000 --> 27:05.680
and he is the one who is worshipped all over the world,

27:05.840 --> 27:09.280
is already written in the Devi Mahatmayam if you read it,

27:09.440 --> 27:13.360
is all clearly written about him how he became an egg

27:13.520 --> 27:16.680
