This one is a very big blessing to us that we all have

29:45.760 --> 29:49.960
this Muladhara Chakra now put into proper thing.

29:50.120 --> 29:53.160
When you sit on the ground also it helps more

29:53.320 --> 29:59.371
because the mother of Shri Ganesha

29:59.531 --> 30:03.291
is this Prithvi, is this earth, the mother earth

30:03.451 --> 30:06.880
and that’s why we should look after the mother earth.

30:07.040 --> 30:09.040
We don’t look after the mother earth.

30:09.200 --> 30:12.520
We don’t understand the value of mother earth.

30:12.680 --> 30:16.640
Actually in Indian culture it is that

30:16.800 --> 30:19.800
when you are getting up in the morning,

30:19.960 --> 30:24.880
you must say Namaskar to the Mother earth

30:25.040 --> 30:29.320
because saying that I bow to you, O, Mother earth

30:29.480 --> 30:32.560
because I am touching you with my feet.

30:32.720 --> 30:35.040
Such respect you should have for Mother earth,

30:35.200 --> 30:36.920
then you won’t exploit it,

30:37.080 --> 30:40.680
you won’t have today’s problems of pollution and this and that.

30:40.840 --> 30:43.680
It all comes out of our ignorance

30:43.840 --> 30:48.240
that the Mother earth is the mother of Shri Ganesha

30:48.400 --> 30:52.080
who’s chakra we have got as Mooladhara.

30:52.240 --> 30:56.720
If you understand this you will be able to understand,

30:56.880 --> 30:59.800
what is to be done.

30:59.960 --> 31:02.880
The mother earth itself we should look after,

31:03.040 --> 31:06.640
we can glorify her, we can beautify her,

31:06.800 --> 31:09.040
we can do all kinds of things

31:09.200 --> 31:14.720
but the way we are exploiting the mother earth is a wrong idea,

31:14.880 --> 31:19.560
is very wrong because it is harming us with pollution.

31:19.720 --> 31:22.800
To cut down the trees, to cut down every thing

31:22.960 --> 31:27.520
that mother has produced and just to use it for money

31:27.680 --> 31:29.560
is a very wrong thing.

31:29.720 --> 31:33.320
One should think about it and when you cut one tree also

31:33.480 --> 31:35.480
you should put another one there.

31:35.640 --> 31:39.000
That is the beauty of the Mother earth,

31:39.160 --> 31:43.600
all the greenery, every thing is the beauty of the Mother earth.

31:43.760 --> 31:51.200
Many people have no interest in gardening or in nature, no interest.

31:51.360 --> 31:54.560
I don’t know how they live but they do

31:54.720 --> 32:00.720
